      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/241eba6e4c00020975cf91170050f435_8220330786606602149.png",
                "id": "talent79170",
                "key": "拂云出手",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "拂云出手"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>生成<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">飞云旗阵</span>，本角色附属<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">旋云护盾</span>并<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span>：<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">长枪开相</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/b7b312b24d3122cbdc5697f8f6f8dd71_7108678805650426048.png",
                "id": "talent61357",
                "key": "旋云开相",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "旋云开相"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素伤害</span>，生成3层<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">飞云旗阵</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/a63a85773eeaa24ce61231eec6b6dd10_7721007929422697207.png",
                "id": "talent53219",
                "key": "破嶂见旌仪",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "破嶂见旌仪"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>和已附着的元素发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（冰）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（水）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（火）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">岩元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">结晶（雷）</span>：本伤害<span>+1，我方出战角色获得1点护盾（可叠加，最多2点）。</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_8624920477617678711.png",
                "id": "talent55000",
                "key": "岩元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "岩元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">飞云旗阵</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方角色进行普通攻击时：</span>造成的伤害+1。</p><p>如果我方手牌数量不多于1，则此技能少花费1个元素骰。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到4次）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">旋云护盾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>准备技能期间：提供2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">护盾</span>，保护所附属的角色。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">长枪开相</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFE699\">岩元素伤害</span>；如果本回合中我方<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span>或<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">调和</span>过至少1张牌，则此伤害+1。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">护盾</span></strong></p><p>此护盾所保护的角色受到伤害时，将会消耗护盾来抵消伤害。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">准备技能</span></strong><br>有些技能无法被直接使用，而是需要一定次数的行动轮来进行<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>。</p><p>轮到一位牌手行动时，如果该牌手的「出战角色」正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能，则跳过该牌手的行动：如果技能已经完成<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>，角色将会在此时直接使用此技能。（此类需要<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>的技能，无法触发「使用技能后」效果。）</p><p>只有「出战角色」才能<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能；如果正在<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>技能的「出战角色」被切换到后台，技能的<span style=\"color: white\">准备</span>就会被打断。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">舍弃</span></strong></p><p>通过行动牌或角色技能的效果，将行动牌从手牌或牌库中弃置。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">调和</span></strong></p><p>为了进行元素调和，而将行动牌从手牌中弃置。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_3185108473308970764.png",
